      "title": "Bandula is the Acting Minister of Education",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Bandula Gunawardena, Minister of Transport, Highways and Mass Media has been appointed as the Acting Minister of Education.",
        "That was due to the Minister of Education Susil Premajayantha going abroad on an official visit."
